rComments: Cool prof!  Tells stories and gives lots of good examples.  Gives out pop-quizzes so come to class.  Tests aren't so bad if you review the class notes.  Overall good class!

His class was easy as long as you showed up for it.  Had random quizes, but were extremely easy if you were in class.  Tests were easy and lecture notes could be found online a week before the test.  Test questions came directly from the lecture notes.  Was extremely interested in the subject and brought in a lot of pictures, movies, ect.
